    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and there is a small tear in the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will eventually need attention for a slow oil leak and some suspension creaks. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character and DIY maintenance.",
