      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this beauty looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor today! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and is in truly flawless condition. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here\u2014it drives like an absolute dream. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love with how perfect it is!",
